<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Inscription confirmée – Saleté Sincère</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Kalam:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/custom.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-[#0B0B0B] text-[#F2F2EF] font-sans min-h-screen">
  
  {{!-- Header --}}
  <header class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-4">
    <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-brush font-bold text-[#F2F2EF] hover:text-[#D6B977] transition">Saleté Sincère</a>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
      <a class="text-sm text-[#D6B977] underline hover:text-[#B99E5A] transition" href="/">Retour à l'accueil</a>
    </div>
  </header>
  
  {{!-- Main container --}}
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 lg:py-20">
      {{!-- Success celebration --}}
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 lg:w-24 lg:h-24 bg-[#D6B977] rounded-full mb-6">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 lg:w-12 lg:h-12 text-[#0B0B0B]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-brush font-bold text-[#F2F2EF] mb-6">Inscription confirmée !</h1>
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-[#D6B977] font-medium italic max-w-md mx-auto">{{tagline}}</p>
      </div>
      
      {{!-- Confirmation message --}}
      <div class="bg-[#0B0B0B] border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8 lg:p-10 text-center">
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-[#F2F2EF] mb-8">
          <strong>Votre inscription est confirmée ! ✅</strong>
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 text-base lg:text-lg text-gray-300">
          <p>Vous recevrez désormais nos newsletters avec :</p>
          <ul class="text-left space-y-3 max-w-md mx-auto">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D6B977]">•</span>
              <span class="ml-2">Les nouveautés audio en avant-première</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D6B977]">•</span>
              <span class="ml-2">Les épisodes longs avant tout le monde</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-[#D6B977]">•</span>
              <span class="ml-2">Les coulisses de Saleté Sincère</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      {{!-- Call to action --}}
      <div class="mt-10 lg:mt-12 text-center space-y-6">
        <a href="{{homeLink}}" class="inline-block px-10 py-4 lg:px-12 lg:py-5 bg-[#D6B977] hover:bg-[#B99E5A] text-[#0B0B0B] font-bold text-lg lg:text-xl rounded-lg transition hover:scale-105">
          Découvrir les histoires
        </a>
        
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">
          <p>En attendant la prochaine newsletter...</p>
          <p>Partagez vos propres histoires</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

  </div>{{!-- End container --}}
  
  <script src="/js/record.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
